# =============================================================================
# .gitignore for Time Clock System
# Covers: ASP.NET Core (C#) + Node.js / React (Vite) + common tooling
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ASP.NET Core / .NET
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
## Build output
bin/
obj/

## Visual Studio files
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## Entity Framework migrations snapshot (keep Migrations folder, ignore snapshots if preferred)
# Uncomment the next line to ignore all generated EF snapshots:
# *ModelSnapshot.cs

## Rider / JetBrains
.idea/
*.DotSettings.user

## Publish profiles & sensitive config
**/Properties/PublishProfiles/
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
appsettings.*.local.json

## User secrets (stored outside repo by design, but guard against accidental inclusion)
secrets.json

## Test results
TestResults/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml
coverage*/

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Node.js / React (Vite)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules/
dist/
dist-ssr/
*.local

## Vite cache
.vite/

## Package manager locks (keep one; ignore the others)
# Uncomment whichever you are NOT using:
# yarn.lock
# pnpm-lock.yaml

## Environment variable files (NEVER commit secrets)
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.env.development
.env.production

## npm / yarn debug logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
lerna-debug.log*

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OS / Editor artifacts
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
## macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

## Windows
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/

## Linux
*~

## VS Code
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json

## Vim / Emacs swap files
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Docker (if added later)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
docker-compose.override.yml
